sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant K8s as Kubernetes
    participant Service as Flask Service
    participant Tracker as Request Tracker
    participant DB as DB/Redis/RabbitMQ

    K8s->>Service: SIGTERM
    Service->>Service: set shutting_down=true
    Service->>Service: wait for LB deregistration delay
    loop until timeout or zero requests
        Service->>Tracker: check active request count
        Tracker-->>Service: active requests remaining
    end
    Service->>DB: close database and broker connections
    Service-->>K8s: exit cleanly
